channel.description:
[center][IMG]http://i1270.photobucket.com/albums/jj601/im1prins1/logo2-1.png[/img][/center] [u][center]Tehdevscape v4 is Out.[/center]
[center]Okay, i think there is not much 508 maker's anymore and .. i would want to see them more and here is one base to start making them, so let's hope we get more 508 makers becouse some years ago 508 was everywhere but now is just 700+ ..[/center]
[size=14pt][center]Do Not Release without giving me credits. [/center]
[center]Features :[/center] [center]-clan wars 80% working, works like this : you choose which team u want, and do command : cwred/cwblue and theres peoples fighting game can be on limited time 500 seconds. [/center] [color=red][center]-I made Museum :) -New Starter -Finished New home -Grand exchange -Warrior's Guild -Level thing fixed -::pure[/center] [center]Much more.[/center] ;)
[size=10pt][center]alright.. Now, Thank you all for likeing my 508 projects and others what there was... 639 and some but anyway thanks alot and i hope you like also this![/center]

@tyb97 wrote:

You didn’t do anything.

-clan wars 80% working, works like this : you choose which team u want, and do command : cwred/cwblue and theres peoples fighting game can be on limited time 500 seconds. Finish it, and maximize it's potential.

-I made Museum
Cool.

-New Starter
Changed some item id’s?

-Finished New home
That’s like the first thing a new programmer does when he starts this stuff.

-Grand exchange
Not yours, look at the credits.

/*
 * Class GrandExchange
 *
 * 90% COMPLETED
 *
 * 04/12/2009
 *
 * Created by GatYuri
 */

-Warrior’s Guild
Alright, it’s a start.

-Level thing fixed
Small bugs really don’t deserve recognition.

-::pure
You added a command? Cool?

Much more.
Sure there is.

The packaging and conventions are horrendous, I can’t find anything, fix this, and put effort and time into it next time. I see potential in you, just try next time.
